reviewText: This was purchased for a gift so I did not personally view the DVD, however it did come on time and in good condition as far as the visual of the package. I did not open or watch the DVD, because it was wrapped in cellophane and was for a gift. I would order other merchandise from this vendor.
I always liked Tim Conway when he was with Harvey Korman and Carol Burnett. With them, he was hilarious! Alone, not so much.
